Sentencas: Thin films of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 (LSGMO), an electrolyte material for the solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC), have been prepared by pulsed laser deposition method.
Titulo: Laser ablation of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 -: Plume and film characterization

Sentencas: Preparation of thin films under high vacuum gives amorphous films, which on annealing at 730 degreesC in air give stochiometric thin films.
Titulo: Laser ablation of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 -: Plume and film characterization

Sentencas: Highly oriented, polycrystalline and amorphous films of LSGMO are obtained on SrTiO3 (001), sapphire (0001) and quartz substrates, respectively.
Titulo: Laser ablation of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 -: Plume and film characterization

Sentencas: The ionic conductivity value for the film deposited on sapphire substrate is an order of magnitude larger than for the film deposited on SrTiO3.
Titulo: Laser ablation of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 -: Plume and film characterization

Sentencas: The plume composition is analyzed by a mass spectrometer.
Titulo: Laser ablation of La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.85 -: Plume and film characterization
